Installing or upgrading to WIEN2k 18.2, refer to the WIEN2k website [ http://susi.theochem.tuwien.ac.at/ ].

Patches for WIEN2k 18.2
-----------------------

- Place atom_read.patch into $WIENROOT/SRC_dstart
- Apply the patch with: patch -b atom_read.F atom_read.patch
- Recompile
Description: Parallel dstart (dstart -p) clmsum fix.
Reference: https://www.mail-archive.com/wien@zeus.theochem.tuwien.ac.at/msg17838.html

- Place Makefile.orig.patch into $WIENROOT/SRC_cif2struct
- Apply the patch with: patch -b Makefile.orig Makefile.orig.patch 
- In .siteconfig, do a Save and Quit of the Compiling Option, then Recompile
Description: Removes "ifort: warning #10315: specifying -lm before files may supersede the Intel(R) math library and affect performance
" when using the Intel Fortran compil$WIENROOTer (ifort).
Reference: https://www.mail-archive.com/wien@zeus.theochem.tuwien.ac.at/msg17807.html

- Place ScaleDiag.patch into $WIENROOT/SRC_mixer
- Apply the patch with: patch -b ScaleDiag.F ScaleDiag.patch
- Recompile
Description: Fixes Jacbian to Jacobian so that the mixer does not crash.
Reference: https://www.mail-archive.com/wien@zeus.theochem.tuwien.ac.at/msg17863.html

- Place seclr4.patch into $WIENROOT/SRC_lapw1
- Apply the patch with: patch -b seclr4.F seclr4.patch
- Recompile
Description: Enables use of ELPA versions from 2017 and onward.
Reference: https://www.mail-archive.com/wien@zeus.theochem.tuwien.ac.at/msg17832.html

- Place siteconfig_lapw.patch into $WIENROOT
- Apply the patch with: patch -b siteconfig_lapw siteconfig_lapw.patch
Description: Changes script from csh to tcsh.  For systems that do not use a csh symbolic link to tcsh,
the script stops with a "Word too long" error on "alias update_makefiles".
Reference: https://www.mail-archive.com/wien@zeus.theochem.tuwien.ac.at/msg17866.html